6000|$|I {{knew the}} long words would impress their simple souls with {{a belief that}} I was {{actually}} praying; <b>and</b> <b>I</b> <b>was</b> <b>right,</b> for every man of them pulled his hat off, and stood staring {{at me with a}} mixed look of reverence, incredulity, and astonishment--but not for long. For before I could say amen, yours truly, or anything, that entire body of water shot upward five hundred feet into the air, as smooth as a column of crystal, curled over in broad green cataracts, falling outward with a jar and thunder like the explosion of a thousand subterranean cannon, then surging and swirling back to the centre, one steaming, writhing mass of snowy foam! ...|$|E
